{"tid":88961,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係咪唔識行迴旋處？","createTime":"2017-01-21T04:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T08:56:12.000Z","uid":22815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44de3927dd6638fecca3ff327364948956e2b96b","tid":88961,"uid":22815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"係觀塘條迴旋處個撚個都行外圈，搞撚到塞撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母，搞到我本身行內圈去第三個出口出唔撚到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:係外國揸開，見翻到黎冇野做借左個friend架車揸左陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知中撚左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa92e50895021dbb0f941bc24583cd71973b817","tid":88961,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"個個都自撚私"},{"pid":"b32970d5aa75fc9209e701b5170bb765f6356577","tid":88961,"uid":22815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個都自撚私</blockquote><br />\non撚9搞到內圈長期冇人"},{"pid":"2d890047fd97121febe69501620629d1aacef2f1","tid":88961,"uid":30644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:45:04.000Z","msg":"入開源道得外圈先出得，自然塞到出黎"},{"pid":"ccedb54429de60bd83b650f0cc390ec5ceb8ca34","tid":88961,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"根本迴旋處應該只設計一個圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58a955f794d358e4a51005784c0ef9d447ee954","tid":88961,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"香港唔係外國<br />\n個個都係自私狗"},{"pid":"d9255238dfff3415cb30da8700a36e94b6058b2c","tid":88961,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:59:57.000Z","msg":"香港學車都唔洗考回旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541cef728495fadcfe4f6d2b135f232782ffe60e","tid":88961,"uid":29447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:00:39.000Z","msg":"應該強制要考迴旋處"},{"pid":"d8ba5e91b87072f6e7febc36bdef9c11f86cddf6","tid":88961,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:03:19.000Z","msg":"因為個個都外圈L, 入左去會出唔番黎， 不停loop, 就無人再入內圈"},{"pid":"046e4d06928f4445710bac0e82facbb3fe6761ba","tid":88961,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:07:30.000Z","msg":"舊式情有可原, 香港好多地方車流量太大唔適合迴旋處, 冇位嘅話可能燈位(eg SPUI)仲好"},{"pid":"3bcd6cbfa1b638ca654defe22785bcc30dbed12d","tid":88961,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊式情有可原, 香港好多地方車流量太大唔適合迴旋處, 冇位嘅話可能燈位(eg SPUI)仲好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊式跟本on鳩, 外圈實唔讓內圈, 事實上想讓都有D危險, D線都劃到一撞就好似內圈cut線錯. 新式好清楚, 上次有車唔想讓都理撚得佢, 撞左實係佢賠, 結果條友避到差D炒."},{"pid":"37e435ff8c3355206b80226b9a30a7f86c82027a","tid":88961,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:22:16.000Z","msg":"唔識cut迴旋處咪兜多2,3個圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要打燈姐<br />\n左燈入左燈出"},{"pid":"c2718cb68033c0ef20f3c1f905bc6ae8eaa449db","tid":88961,"uid":8909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n好多車手由內圈一野bump 出去<br />\n唔理外圈有無車<br />\n內圈撚覺得自己大撚晒<br />\n攪到外圈行緊時又要重dup<br />\n後車又一野隊埋外圈重dup個架車個pat pat<br />\n其實真係好撚危險<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5846768f737322d721cb8fd7cbb91c0fa676fdee","tid":88961,"uid":8495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識cut迴旋處咪兜多2,3個圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要打燈姐<br />\n左燈入左燈出</blockquote><br />\n左燈入？"},{"pid":"f3e64a6e5a3c8732e65d0c301c0a8a057465583a","tid":88961,"uid":50020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔識cut迴旋處咪兜多2,3個圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要打燈姐<br />\n左燈入左燈出</blockquote><br />\n左燈入？</blockquote><br />\n左燈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3a65d18684725ba948bbdef07de17f16646bfb","tid":88961,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔識cut迴旋處咪兜多2,3個圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要打燈姐<br />\n左燈入左燈出</blockquote><br />\n左燈入？</blockquote><br />\n左燈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n左燈入代表你係第一個出口出<br />\n右燈代表其他出口/右邊出口 (直行我多數唔打)"},{"pid":"0447a4651352109fa83ca178b58d48fac55ce406","tid":88961,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n左燈入？</blockquote><br />\n左燈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n左燈入代表你係第一個出口出<br />\n右燈代表其他出口/右邊出口 (直行我多數唔打)</blockquote><br />\n以前駕駛學院都係教出路口/迴旋處都係打左燈<br />\n但我慣打右燈出路口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065d6c8abb21967570499c75ec29dbf80b4e04ec","tid":88961,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T03:20:15.000Z","msg":"你係最外線入 係打左燈入喎<br />\n打完熄左佢<br />\n我見巴士佬都係咁打法"},{"pid":"ae1209a6e3d90d5c68b60955f9b7dd76bfd12710","tid":88961,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係最外線入 係打左燈入喎<br />\n打完熄左佢<br />\n我見巴士佬都係咁打法</blockquote><br />\n靠害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n運輸署官方講法係<br />\n下個出口出就左入左出<br />\n直行出口就唔打燈入左出<br />\n右轉出口就右燈入到臨出前左出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e259d8628f623653d3ea3a6c82e5d8737024ee9","tid":88961,"uid":14570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"香港試新式迴旋處試左十萬世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係就快啲統一"},{"pid":"c7021ca43d3d80ff9b4d37a778face6234c94447","tid":88961,"uid":41765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港學車都唔洗考回旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n油塘要，，，"},{"pid":"4af2929baf3b379d956e04be7de06d5742b95d01","tid":88961,"uid":54327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:18:38.000Z","msg":"香港人揸車大撚把淨係識考車唔識行車。<br />\n<br />\n再講多次，又到過年又到傻仔一窩蜂喪屍出籠，咁多位巴打路上小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132ce2bc74fbceaf06c503a7828b2df341a85edb","tid":88961,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"話鳩知運輸處點講<br />\n點都行左線入外圈包冇死錯人<br />\n根本迴旋處就唔應該有兩條lane <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028b789d22f9f7c9f965e7552c08aca74dde85e7","tid":88961,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"香港人行迴旋處已經係獨有文化嚟<br />\n跟運輸處d官方方法係會出唔到迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,唔理新式舊式,一律當新式行就得<br />\n因為原理上,岩岩過左個出口,總會有車轉出出口,即刻cut線食返佢個位就出到"},{"pid":"f0ec772c3dfe54b9c85a824b5c503300cc3b6029","tid":88961,"uid":18350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"次次內圈出，打哂燈，外圈架車仲要加速衝上黎閘你。<br />\n咁大家鬥行外圈囉<br />\nbtw同意全部改單圈或者剷平佢變燈位"}]}